Program: The History Hour
Title: Adopted By The Man Who Killed My Family
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswqmj
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 11 Dec 2018
A child survivor of a Guatemalan army massacre during the country's brutal civil war, the women who cleared up post war Berlin, plus Armenia's 1988 earthquake, how Bokassa became Emperor of the Central African Republic, and Angela Merkel's rise to power. Photo: Ramiro as a child in Guatemala (R.Osorio) Show less